bt.module

Annotation Type MessageHandlers


  • @Target(value={PARAMETER,FIELD,METHOD})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface MessageHandlers
    Annotates individual message handlers, that work with core BitTorrent message types.

    Each message type is assigned a unique numeric ID, thus annotated value should be a Map<Integer, MessageHandler>.

    Since:
    1.0
